I '''Paul Gardner Allen''' (mibait Eneru 21, 1953) metung yang Americanung entrepreneur nung nu kambe nang [[Bill Gates]] mitatag keng [[Microsoft]]  at metung ya kareng [[List of billionaires (2009)|pekamakualtang tau keti yatu]].  

Iya ing mitatag ampong chairman ning [[Vulcan Inc.]], nung nu iti privadu yang asset management a cumpania, ampong chairman ning [[Charter Communications]]. I Allen atin ya naman multi-billion dollar investment portfolio nung nu kayabe makataya keng [[Moxi|Digeo]], real estate holdings, ampong maiggit a 40 aliwang technology, media, ampong content a cumpania. I Allen iya mu rin ing mikibandi kareng atlung aliwang  professional sports teams: ing [[Seattle Seahawks]] na ning [[National Football League]]<ref name="seahawks" />, ing [[Portland Trail Blazers]] na ning [[National Basketball Association]]<ref name="trailblazers" />, ampo ing  [[Seattle Sounders FC]] franchise keng [[Major League Soccer]] a megumpisang mamialung keng 2009 season.<ref name="soccer" />


